    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，触发源很重要。从空闲状态到解析状态，应该是由车队管理模块发起DECODE操作。而从解析到提取的转换，也是车队管理触发的AUTO操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "parsing",
        "DECODE",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前两个转换画出来：idle到parsing标注DECODE [Logistics_FleetManagement]，parsing到extracting标注AUTO [Logistics_FleetManagement]。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
