      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这两条转换。现在状态流转是：idle→parsing→extracting→tracing→computing。还需要考虑异常处理或者重置机制吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
